properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 18 at 3:44AM EST until January 20 at 6:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...West to northwest wind 15 to 20 knots with gusts up to 25
or 30 knots on Sunday and Sunday night. Waves 2 to 3 feet are
expected.

* WHERE...Upper Delaware Bay.

* WHEN...From 6:00 AM Sunday until 6:00 AM Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating a small
vessel, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM SUNDAY TO 6 AM EST MONDAY
